<p><i><b>Creatures</b></i> is an <a href="/wiki/Artificial_life" title="Artificial life">artificial life</a> (alife) <a href="/wiki/Computer_program" title="Computer program">computer program</a> series, created in the mid-1990s by <a href="/wiki/England" title="England">English</a> <a href="/wiki/Computer_science" title="Computer science">computer scientist</a> <a href="/wiki/Steve_Grand" title="Steve Grand">Steve Grand</a> whilst working for the <a href="/wiki/Cambridge" title="Cambridge">Cambridge</a> <a href="/wiki/Computer_game" title="Computer game" class="mw-redirect">computer games</a> developer <a href="/wiki/Millennium_Interactive" title="Millennium Interactive">Millennium Interactive</a>. The program is one of the few games (as of 2008) to employ <a href="/wiki/Machine_learning" title="Machine learning">machine learning</a>.</p>
